Class
Python is an object-oriented language, so the class is an essential concept and basic of data types.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Assignment Statement
example1: a=b; //make b value equals to a, give the value of b to the intance a.
example2: c=2; //make 2 equals to a , give the value 2 to the instance c.
error1: 122=a; //SyntaxError: cannot assign to literal.
error2:   1=b; //SyntaxError: cannot assign to literal.
